Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 是醉拳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}從昨天電視中播的電影裡看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦哦 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這藉口編得跟麻耶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有好多拿著花的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天是高中的畢業典禮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話說回來 志願該怎麼填呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}已經到了不得不考慮的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說到畢業典禮 心愛她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還沒有畢業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能順利升班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是在擔心這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我覺得沒問題喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我只是說說看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃QAQ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真有問題啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<OP>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}被畢業典禮感動到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嚇了我們一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}而且 一想到我來到這個小鎮如今已經快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}時間真是轉瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 在這在這
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你怎麼哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們是已經約好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 為了慶祝升班想開個茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}找到家不錯的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃你們也一起來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對別的店見異思遷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要從Rabbit House畢業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}滿座了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和高中生組的座位分開了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想像那樣變得更加成熟些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}成熟些？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像是對後輩說「一起去喝茶吧」這樣自然的邀請她們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能不能很自然的邀請到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼惠 我們來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你 你真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一… 一起去喝茶怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是可疑的搭訕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路喝茶的樣子跟大小姐一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺很成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想成為那樣的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個券還可以用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是免費券吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是精打細算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}令人憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}總覺得妹妹好像被人搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有沒有成熟些了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}變得稍微優雅些了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是您的下午茶套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們沒點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是那邊的客人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這裡不是酒吧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯哼哼 看起來很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是姐姐給可愛的妹妹們的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我開動……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我聽說吃這些是有順序的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好像是從三明治開始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還是司康餅來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這要不吃出點樣子來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就沒法成為成熟的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們還是學學紗路她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在吃熱狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對面也上來和我們一樣的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是模仿的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我感受到一股羡慕的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 也許是我們正被觀察著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}觀察…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}觀察我們是不是值得尊敬的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太誇張了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你信了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們覺得我對相對論的說明好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是想展現自己的腦袋頂呱呱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要說到狹義相對論和廣義相對論的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我比較喜歡狹義相對論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這話題竟然給接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這 這年頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}把般若心經背下不過是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}連紗路也來！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}廣義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說到宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狹義相對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過應該是想在開吃之前好好聊一聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們也得說些成熟的話題才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 最近我第一次讓老哥去幫我跑腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這哪裡成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}下 下次我就去Rabbit House的酒吧逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我就熬一下夜試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐我是不會允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}被聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在喝下午茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看起來好歡樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}您知道這東西的吃法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通地吃不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對呀 普通地吃就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐的普通估計和我們的不太一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}難道我很特殊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃她們在和青山小姐聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話題好像挺嚴肅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}她們肯定是在向青山小姐尋求意見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}關於什麼的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}經過她們的觀察覺得我們不值得尊敬什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃她們要我來觀察觀察各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}別說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}相 相對論嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狹義和廣義和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}色 色即是空 空 空即是色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我比較喜歡宇宙弦理論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呀 真巧 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大 大家都這樣嗎 好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也是 我挺喜歡宇宙弦理論的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為不知道下午茶怎麼喝才觀察的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學著學著你的動作就跟到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒必要這麼鑽牛角尖的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可是 對於成熟的女性來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這些東西只要吃的開心就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}禮儀也只是為了讓彼此更舒暢才存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}教官之訓導 深入我心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 她們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有空位子了所以拜託店員合併起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用抽籤來分位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可別為了自己和晚輩們坐一起出老千啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我可是很公平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}人家光是能和大家一起開茶會就已經很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來 智乃也吃吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 也吃吃這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是分到了最遠的座位而已嘛 別這麼沮喪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 好遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}儘管問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狹義相對論和廣義相對論有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}誰叫你們那麼逞能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要更努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再來再來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你到底想幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要變得更有姐姐樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃 我來幫你拿書包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和姐姐客氣什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我沒客氣什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那我來背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}客氣什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是姐姐寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這次的回信速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 就算是春假也不能睡懶覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}玩偶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早安 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早飯要涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和平時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用完早飯後　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我會告訴你狹義相對論和廣義相對論之間的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的樣子很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}的確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比平時更加機敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是在幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摸提比也摸地更加機敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}攬客的動作也更機敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}帶您入座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好紳士～～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}搞得像別家店一樣了 請別繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這麼一說和平時瀏海的方向也反過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可能是冒充的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}毛茸茸 毛茸茸 毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}毛茸茸天國！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個應該還是會忍不住抱過來才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不認真工作是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然不知道為什麼但是非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}微妙的受挫感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}如果努力過頭發燒了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我才剛這麼想！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼在這之前不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}後天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}後天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐要過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是說想讓姐姐看到自己努力的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要更加努力的去做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要好好的做智乃的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的姐姐很嚴厲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}安心啦 很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然我也有兩個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是姐姐教訓他們 讓他們聽話的樣子很帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}教訓什麼的 她是馴獸師嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}調教 我接下來會被怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}發抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來如此 所以才憧憬著姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}身為老么也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}讓她看看你的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 好羡慕心愛有那麼多兄弟姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世也要作為我的妹妹介紹給姐姐哦 和智乃一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通的朋友就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎樣才能看起來很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想讓姐姐看到我的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}總之 先讓從剛才開始就抖個不停的智乃安下心來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}要被揉個不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒關係 有我陪著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒～關係 有我陪著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}住手 住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明是一樣的台詞 但差距這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對了 理世你們稍微犯點蠢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這樣就顯得心愛很可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}逆向思考？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 已經說了要幫助她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}知道了 我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦咦咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想點餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 咖 咖啡的種類我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我數學很爛 不小心訂了一噸的罐裝咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你這個冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 麵包能用火焰噴射器烤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇啊啊啊 我看不下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這可是為了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}接下來該換我們上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請多指教 Sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 這裡還有灰塵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺有什麼要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要接住這個飛盤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}汪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3\an8}好啦 我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話說回來 這是什麼的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為想變得像姐姐一樣 所以請模仿一下妹妹的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐 我想吃麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}幫我做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一會就來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這要持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}直到心愛察覺到這毫無意義為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天謝謝大家為我忙這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}幾杯咖啡拿鐵 不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 這是心愛畫的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比我第一次給我的時候進步多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一直都在看反而沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這不就是你有在成長的證明嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好棒好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 今後我會更加發奮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想看3D咖啡拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算作為店員進步了 作為姐姐也還差得很遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}3D咖啡拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是提比而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不管過多久都成不了一個可靠的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎？ 我覺得心愛已經是個很好的姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖說如此 但是光說不做出實際表現的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛一聽說姐姐要來也太焦慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一般心不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃也是 明明近來跟心愛玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路你是在擔心心愛和智乃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我只是覺得心愛應該更自信一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那紗路也要拿出自信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊？ 怎麼說到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我很擔心紗路你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼要擔心我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}闊別一年的再會嗎 應該很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}又期待又擔憂吧 連那個心愛都慌成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}作為姐姐的成長嗎？ 真是自尋煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那種東西 只要是親人 無須刻意展示也能感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你偶爾也會說些正經話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這裡也有個自大的兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}差不多到車站了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不去接真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}她信裡說會自己來店裡的 叫心愛專心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是這樣的吧？ 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心…愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛緊張得僵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 你還得接客呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}信裡不是叫你專心工作的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 喂 心愛 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}心愛的姐姐…是個怎樣的人呢？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這下後果嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}具體有什麼後果？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個嘛 反正很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}很？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是不得了的意思
